# RGBJunkie effects API

See **`EFFECTS_API.md`**.

- **`exportedHtml`** / **`exportedHtmlUpdatedAt`** on Firestore **`projects`** — written from **`js/main.js`** on save, share, zip export, and from **`?adminBackfillExport=1`** (admin iframe only, same **`ADMIN_UID`** as **`admin/admin.js`**).
- **`GET /effects/effect.json`** — **`html`** mirrors **`exportedHtml`** when present; else **`null`**. **`exportPlainUrl`** remains the browser fallback.
- **Admin** (`**/admin/**`) — backfill loads builder iframes sequentially; requires Firestore rules allowing admin **`update`** on others’ projects for those fields.
